default build (= OWB for core and TomEE for ee6):
mvn clean package

build to test core with Weld:
mvn clean package -PWeld

build to test core with OWB (explicitly):
mvn clean package -POWB

build to test the web-app:
mvn clean package -PDeltaSpikeTest

build web-archive for GlassFish3 (+ Weld)
mvn clean package -PWeld -PGlassFish


build web-archive for JBoss AS7 (+ Weld)
mvn clean package -PWeld -PJBoss
